    <input type="text" value="Fruit">
</div>

</div>

<div id="recipe">
<pre>
4 cups 2% reduced-fat milk
½ cup sugar
1 teaspoon vanilla extract

Combine all ingredients in a bowl, stirring with a whisk until sugar dissolves.
Pour into an 8-inch square glass or ceramic baking dish.
Cover and freeze until partially frozen (about 1 hour).
Scrape with a fork, crushing any lumps.
Freeze, scraping with a fork every hour, 2 hours or until completely frozen.
</pre>
